  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "According to <https://www.debian.org/doc/debian-policy/ch-controlfields.html#s-f-version>, if the upstream_version contains a hyphen (as in `7.1.0-preview.3`), then the syntax requires a debian_revision (such as `1.debian.11`).\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://www.debian.org/doc/debian-policy/ch-controlfields.html#s-f-version\">5. Control files and their fields — Debian Policy Manual v4.5.0.2</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
